Quizy is a quiz framework written on top of the authentication framework - phpUserAuth (http://iambot.net/projects/phpuserauth/). Writing a mini quiz framework on top of the authentication framework itself makes it very secure.
=======
Quizy is a quiz framework written on top of the authentication framework - phpUserAuth (http://iambot.net/projects/phpuserauth/). Writing a mini quiz framework on top of the
authentication framework itself makes it very secure.
>>>>>>> 05abfd9c2c37ee0e37f797e99c373f71c17256e8

